title: Bug 19458[Navigator] Copy Project dialog UI problems
description: When attempting to copy a project in the Navigator, an issue arises with the UI elements displaying in red text.
OB: Upon selecting the project name as 'test', an unexpected static text validation error is displayed within the dialog.
EB: The dialog should not exhibit any red text or validation errors when selecting the project name.
SR:
1. Open the Navigator interface.
2. Attempt to copy a project.
3. Choose the project name as 'test' and observe the dialog for any unexpected red text or validation errors.
